Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:23.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}于是牵住了伙伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:29.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这样的话将永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:34.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年无忧的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:41.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论如何都想要告诉你
