Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:54.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:58.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一个个渐渐离去
